W:  Because of the dreams flying, distance will become closer;
W:  Because of the North Star guiding, true love will be awakening.
W:  Crossing the border of the night comes the eternal love;
W:  I will stand in the dawn before our meeting, waiting for you to come.
W:
W:  Because of the sound of blooming, the winter will be far away;
W:  Because of the footprint of the sunlight, the warmth will reach the earth.
W:  Marching toward the rising sun comes the forever bright horizon;
W:  I will be your perpetual sunshine, accompanying you in floating clouds and light breeze.
W:
W:  When parting comes again, my dear, do not feel sad;
W:  I will still be able to see and believe even though there is no light.
W:  Happiness is an appointment, it will someday be fulfilled;
W:  I wish I were the only love you've had, who forever stays in your heart.
